Windows Migration Electronic Email Notice Cc martino PLEASE DO NOT ERASE THE EMAIL PLEASE RESPOND Project Gem is approaching and Enron is going global with Windows Migration They are trying to assist RAC in implementing the Migration in a successful fashion To do this they have requested an inventory of each computer within RAC The Network managers have created a simplier and easier way to do this Each Group within RAC will have a Contact Person to work closely with them His name is Lee Steele Lee Steele Manager of Enron Networks will be sending each of us an email regarding the Windows Migration He would like an inventory of each employees computer applications On the said email that each of you receive from Lee PLEASE open the link from your own computer According to Lee this is very important because once you open the email by clicking on the link it will automatically list each application you have so again please pay close attention to the Email from Lee Steele Lee Look forward to receiving your email Thank you in advance Dorothy Forwarded by Dorothy YoungbloodHOUECT on AM From William S Bradford PM To Dorothy CT cc Karen K CT Subject Windows Migration Electronic Email Notice Please get me on the distribution Bill Forwarded by William S BradfordHOUECT on PM From Karen K Heathman PM To William S CT cc Subject Windows Migration Electronic Email Notice FYI
